the .kshrc file, you can use these emacs commands:

Ctrl-P:previous command
Ctrl-N:next command
Ctrl-A:beginning of line
Ctrl-E:end of line
Ctrl-b:char backward
Ctrl-f:char forward
Meta-b:word backward
(if your keyboard does'n have the Meta key, use Escape instead)
Meta-f:word forward
Ctrl-h (or Backspace): delete char backward
Ctrl-d:delete char forward
Meta-h:delete word backward
Meta-d:delete word forward
Ctrl-k:delete to end of line
